      <title>债务狂潮过后，投资者对印度影子银行的疲软持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/investors-wary-of-weaker-indian-shadow-banks-after-debt-binge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者对印度影子银行债务的选择性越来越强，这意味着在 2024 年该行业多年来外债销售额创下新高后，市场上的小型企业将面临麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/investors-wary-of-weaker-indian-shadow-banks-after-debt-binge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国收益率曲线趋平，央行债券购买成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/china-s-flatter-yield-curve-is-putting-focus-on-pboc-bond-buying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行决定暂停购买债券，这加剧了短期利率的上升和收益率曲线的趋平，引发人们对央行可能恢复购买政府债券的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/china-s-flatter-yield-curve-is-putting-focus-on-pboc-bond-buying</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
